title: Pixel 4a5g preorder gift for Germany
content:
Hi guys,

I just wanted to ask, whether the 4a5g bundle with the Bose headphones will also be available in Germany? I'm a little hesitant, as the promotion says, that the bundle comes with the 4a5g OR the 5 and clicking on the Terms and conditions reveals, that UK/Ireland are qualified for the 4a5g whereas FR/GER aren't (only 5). Is this a mistake by Google or is Germany actually not qualified for the 4a5g bundle? I'm so confused, I even got a notification about it...but yeah...
